info.description:
[![](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/stdin.svg?maxAge=3600)](https://pypi.org/project/stdin/) [![](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-Unlicense-blue.svg?longCache=True)](https://unlicense.org/) ### Installation ```bash $ [sudo] pip install stdin ``` #### Examples ```bash $ printf "stdin text" | python -c "import stdin;print(stdin.size())" 10 $ echo "stdin text" | python -c "import stdin;print(stdin.size())" 11 ``` ```bash python -c "import stdin;print(stdin.read())" $ echo "stdin text" | python -c "import stdin;print(stdin.read())" stdin text ```
